###############################################################################
## LOPIT Analysis: SVM for Joined TMT Data (Lojza's aggregated format)
## Matches Lojza's filtering: filterRows=42, NAs imputed per-replicate, no row-norm
## All 42 quanti columns used as a single dataset (3 reps x 14 fractions)
## Fixes vs prior version:
##   1. Multi-protein group rows kept as separate entries (Lojza-style, ~4910 rows)
##   2. NAs imputed by per-replicate fraction-wise median (not replaced with 0)
##   3. 2D t-SNE: both static PNG and interactive HTML outputs
## Author: Abhishek Prakash Shinde
###############################################################################

